## Notes
- Tool: iLovePDF Edit PDF
- Toolbar Options:
    - **Select/Mouse**: Move/Resize elements.
    - **Add Text**: Font options (Font family, Size, Color, Bold, Italic, Underline, Alignment).
    - **Edit Existing Text**: Modify text within the original PDF layer.
    - **Add Image**: Import from Device, Google Drive, or Dropbox. Properties: Resize, Rotate, Transparency, Order (Front/Back).
    - **Shapes**: Rectangle, Circle, Line. Properties: Fill color, Stroke color, Stroke size, Transparency.
    - **Draw (Pencil)**: Freehand drawing. Properties: Color, Thickness, Transparency.
    - **Add Symbols & Emojis**: Library of icons.
- Other Features:
    - **Page Thumbnails**: View and navigate pages.
    - **Undo/Redo**: History management.
    - **Zoom**: Zoom in/out, fit to width.
    - **Safe Storage**: Encrypted processing.
    - **Cloud Integration**: GDrive & Dropbox.
    - **Mobile Friendly**: Works on browsers and app.


